title: The Columbia Trail Masters Episode IX
text: Home » travel » The Columbia Trail Masters Episode IX The Columbia Trail Masters Episode IX July 28, 2015 10:48 am AMA events and Columbia Thailand are delighted and proud to announce the Columbia Trail Masters episode IX. Date: 2 August, 2015 Venue: Chakapong Reservoir, Kao Ito, Prachinburi (Near Nakhon Nayok) The-Columbia-Trail-Masters-Episode-IXThis is a must-try trail running experience in Prachin Buri, which offers a wealth of outdoor activities. The event features different distances, from 50km, 25km, 10km to 3km for families and children. A 3km fun run is available for racer under 15 years. Schedule
